				<p>Yours Truly</p>
				<p>Inhaste</p>
				<p><persName role="author">Isaac Hart</persName></p>
				<p>I was at rehearsal on<lb/> <date>Sunday</date> last.  <persName>Lehache<add>&#63;</add></persName> is<lb/> the Leader.  The music is beautiful &#38; well sang<lb/> The synagogue inside is very much like<lb/> the one on <placeName>Rampart St</placeName><lb/> The old pulpit is between the allmoner<lb/> &#38; Nichol</p>
